Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 16:18:19 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] feat(schema): add remote config inheritance via extends
 URL

New `extends:` field in .smoke.yaml fetches a remote base config
(HTTPS, HTTP with warning, file://) and merges it with local config.
Remote provides defaults, local overrides settings and appends tests.
HTTP caching with ETag/Last-Modified headers, cached to
$XDG_CACHE_HOME/cosmo-smoke/. 16 tests covering all schemes,
caching, merge behavior, and error handling.
